genresAdvancedInfo.name: indie psychedelic rock
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Indie psychedelic rock is a genre that blends the trippy, mind-bending sounds of psychedelic rock with the DIY spirit of indie music. It often features swirling guitars, hypnotic rhythms, and dreamy vocals that transport listeners to otherworldly realms and encourage them to explore their own inner landscapes.
